Opening shot: the T-Car rolling on a winding mountain road. It is nighttime, and the
                Tower is visible in the distance. Inside, Raven peeks out from behind Cyborg's seat;
                Robin is next to her.

Pan to Cyborg, who turns to look in the direction of the noise. His eyes go wide;
                cut to the parking lot, where the T-Car is about to peel out with Gizmo still
                driving. A waitress rolls up on her skates.
